  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HeuristicStrategy
    Interface for a heuristic to be provided to a State object
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Action
    Defines one action for the pen plotter.
    Line
    Defines a line in the x-y plane given two endpoints.
    LinesLeftStrategy
    Implementation of a HeuristicStrategy Interface that calculates an appropriate heuristic for a state.
    Plotter
    Takes input from the file specified in the first argument and converts it into a series of lines.
    State
    Stores the properties of a single state, including the lines not yet drawn, the actions taken to get to the state, pen position and the cost.
    StateSearch
    Sets up the initial state and performs an A* Search on it.
